## Step 6 — Disable the GraphQL API (if not using it)

pg_graphql is enabled by default and exposes a `/graphql/v1` endpoint.
If you are not using GraphQL, disable it:

```
Supabase Dashboard → Database → Extensions → pg_graphql → toggle OFF
```

Or via SQL:
```sql
DROP EXTENSION IF EXISTS pg_graphql;
```

